* Motivation

- Usage of mobile devices is growing and has surpassed computer usage.
- It's more common to carry your mobile device than your laptop.

.image http://www.smartinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Mobile-stats-vs-desktop-users-global-550x405.png _ 550

* Features

- Manage passwords (list, create, edit, ...)
- Offline access to your passwords
- SLIP-0016 format (compatible with Trezor PM Chrome extension)

* Tech

- Frontend/UI: React Native (no previous experience)
- Backend: Go (Tesoro library + gomobile)
- Others: Some Java to put things together

